{"title":"Higher Education and Research Bill: impact assessment","public_updated_at":"2016-06-07T14:00:38Z","details":{"tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":["access-to-higher-education"],"topics":[]},"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>These documents consider the impact of the measures set out in the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://services.parliament.uk/bills/2016-17/highereducationandresearch.html\">Higher Education and Research Bill</a> on:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>students</li>\n  <li>higher education providers</li>\n  <li>taxpayers</li>\n  <li>other parts of society</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The impact assessments cover the measures on:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the Teaching Excellence Framework</li>\n  <li>sector entry and the single gateway</li>\n  <li>information sharing</li>\n  <li>student protection</li>\n  <li>establishing the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/office-for-students-business-case\">Office for Students</a>\n</li>\n  <li>deregulating higher education corporations and simplifying governing documents</li>\n  <li>power to enter and inspect</li>\n  <li>alternative finance</li>\n  <li>establishing <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/uk-research-and-innovation-business-case\">UK Research and Innovation (UKRI)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1583601\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/524517/bis-16-264-he-research-bill-impact-assessment.pdf\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/524517/thumbnail_bis-16-264-he-research-bill-impact-assessment.pdf.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/524517/bis-16-264-he-research-bill-impact-assessment.pdf\">Higher Education and Research Bill: summary impact assessment</a></